OL,7,FBut on the eve of the anniversary,
OL,8,FDowning Street said more time was
OL,9,Fneeded to draft the best version of
OL,10,Fthe legislation, which campaigners
OL,11,Fhope will include a legal duty of
OL,12,Fcandour on public authorities.
OL,14,FIn March, it was reported that a
OL,15,Fmeeting between Sir Keir and
OL,16,Fcampaigners had been cancelled, with
OL,17,Fclaims officials were attempting to
OL,18,Fhave the contents of the Bill watered
OL,19,Fdown.
