OL,7,FElkan Abrahamson, solicitor for
OL,8,FBroudie Jackson Canter and director of
OL,9,Fthe Hillsborough Law Now campaign,
OL,10,Fsaid the redrafted version was a
OL,11,F"betrayal" of promises made.
OL,13,FHe said: "We remain largely in the
OL,14,Fdark as to the status of the Bill and
OL,15,Fthe next steps.
OL,17,F"The recent Cabinet Office redraft of
OL,18,Fthe Bill is a betrayal of the promises
OL,19,Fmade by the Government so there must
OL,20,Fbe urgent steps to return to the
OL,21,Foriginal principles.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@JO]uD@JOUyD@AOU
