OL,7,F"We have made it clear to the
OL,8,FGovernment that we will not accept
OL,9,Fanything that falls short of a full
OL,10,FHillsborough Law which includes a duty
OL,11,Fof candour for all public officials.
OL,13,F"We stand ready to assist the
OL,14,FGovernment in delivering the promised
OL,15,Flegislation and urge them to speak to
OL,16,Fus to better understand what is
OL,17,Frequired.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
