OL,7,F"The legislation must deliver what was
OL,8,Fpromised in the coming weeks to ensure
OL,9,Fa lasting legacy for Hillsborough
OL,10,Ffamilies and survivors and to ensure
OL,11,Fothers are not put through the ordeal
OL,12,Fof fighting for truth, justice and
OL,13,Faccountability."
OL,15,FCampaigners are planning to contact
OL,16,Fall MPs by the end of the month.
