OL,3,CFamilies 'betrayed' over Hillsborough
OL,4,CLaw delay on 36th anniversary of
OL,5,Ctragedy
OL,7,F"Despite all the challenges they have
OL,8,Ffaced, they have kept fighting. I
OL,9,Fpromised to bring a Hillsborough Law
OL,10,Fbefore Parliament, with a legal duty
OL,11,Fof candour for public authorities and
OL,12,Fpublic servants, and criminal
OL,13,Fsanctions for anyone who fails to
OL,14,Fcomply. I will deliver on that promise.
OL,16,F"After decades of injustice, we must
OL,17,Fget this legislation right. We must
OL,18,Fmake sure it achieves what the people
OL,19,Fof Liverpool have spent the past
OL,20,Fthirty-six years fighting for.
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@AOU
