OL,7,F"Standing firmly at the side of
OL,8,FHillsborough families, this is what my
OL,9,Fgovernment will deliver."
OL,11,FOn Monday, 14 April, the Prime
OL,12,FMinister's official spokesman said:
OL,13,F"Having consulted with groups over
OL,14,Frecent weeks and months, we believe
OL,15,Fmore time is needed to draft the best
OL,16,Fversion of a Hillsborough Law, but we
OL,17,Fremain fully committed to bringing
OL,18,Fthis legislation at pace, and we'll
OL,19,Fobviously continue to work with them
OL,20,Fin the weeks ahead and provide an
OL,21,Fupdate when we've got it."
