OL,7,FNinety-seven football fans died as a
OL,8,Fresult of a crush at the match between
OL,9,FLiverpool and Nottingham Forest at
OL,10,FHillsborough Stadium in Sheffield.
OL,12,FOn Tuesday, the anniversary will be
OL,13,Fmarked with a minute's silence in
OL,14,FLiverpool and flags on civic buildings
OL,15,Fwill be flown at half staff.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/15
