OL,7,FThe Lord Mayor of Liverpool, Richard
OL,8,FKemp, and council leader Liam Robinson
OL,9,Fwill lead the silence in Exchange
OL,10,FFlags, behind the town hall, before a
OL,11,Fbell is tolled 97 times and an
OL,12,Finstrumental version of You'll Never
OL,13,FWalk Alone is played.
OL,15,FThe original Hillsborough inquest
OL,16,Fverdicts were quashed in 2012
OL,17,Ffollowing the publication of an
OL,18,Findependent panel report and in 2016 a
OL,19,Fjury found victims of the disaster
OL,20,Fwere unlawfully killed amid a number
OL,21,Fof police errors.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/15
