OL,7,FThe match commander on the day, David
OL,8,FDuckenfield, was charged with gross
OL,9,Fnegligence manslaughter in 2017, but
OL,10,Fwas cleared in 2019 at a retrial held
OL,11,Fafter the jury in his first trial was
OL,12,Funable to reach a verdict.
OL,14,FIn 2021, retired officers Donald
OL,15,FDenton and Alan Foster and former
OL,16,Fforce solicitor Peter Metcalf, who
OL,17,Fwere accused of amending statements to
OL,18,Fminimise the blame on South Yorkshire
OL,19,FPolice, were acquitted of perverting
OL,20,Fthe course of justice after a judge
OL,21,Fruled there was no case to answer.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/15
